Transmission of donor illness by stem cell transplantation: should screening be 
different in older donors?

Niederwieser D(1), Gentilini C, Hegenbart U, Lange T, Moosmann P, Pönisch W, 
Al-Ali H, Raida M, Ljungman P, Tyndall A, Urbano-Ispizua A, Lazarus HM, Gratwohl 
