PMID: 15335426 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


419. J Hepatol. 2004 Sep;41(3):446-53. doi: 10.1016/j.jhep.2004.05.013.

Donor age influences 10-year liver graft histology independently of hepatitis C 
virus infection.

Rifai K(1), Sebagh M, Karam V, Saliba F, Azoulay D, Adam R, Castaing D, Bismuth 
H, Reynès M, Samuel D, Féray C.

Author information:
(1)Centre Hépato-Biliaire, Hôpital Paul Brousse, Villejuif Assistance 
